snippet.title: Spectra: PAX East Trailer
snippet.description:
A grimy, neon filled immersive sim set in a dystopian alternate history 1972. Sneak, fight, and trick your way through a beautifully ugly city, and discover the world of Spectra.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2592230/Spectra/
